<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_419" id="208v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_419_r1l20">Hanſen von VVeſternach cʒu Stauffen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_419_r1l21"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> von vveſternach / Vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> . <expan cert="unknown">C</expan> . Seydein <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l22">vvie Jr Jm <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> . j . pellein mit 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒwilch </del> vier kalbfeln </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l23">v̈mbſlagen darynne . ıx ſtück cʒwilchs etliche yltiſch vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l24">fuchſpelg / lxxij ſtück puchſpaums vnd j laden mit puchſ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l25"><expan>pawmin<ex>n</ex></expan> löffeln ſein / aufgehalten habt / darümb der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l26"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒu 
<add><ab facs="#facs_419_line_1596021914374_222">ew </ab></add> kümt . <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l27">ſein habe vnd <expan>kauffmanſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> <expan>wıdergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd vngehindert </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l28">volgen <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> Als etc das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_419" id="208v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hansen von Westernach czu Stauffen</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> von Westernach, uns hat
                                                  <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>
<expan cert="unknown">C.</expan> Seydein,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie ir im
                                                  <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> i pellein mit
                                                vier kalbfeln ümbslagen, darynne ix stück czwilchs,
                                                etliche yltisch und fuchspelg, lxxii stück
                                                puchspaums und i laden mit
                                                  puchs<expan>pawmin<ex>n</ex></expan> löffeln sein,
                                                aufgehalten habt, darümb der
                                                  <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> czu <add>ew</add>
                                                kümt. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                                  <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> sein habe und
                                                  <expan>kauffmans<ex>chaft</ex></expan>
<expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und ungehindert
                                                volgen <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet
                                                  <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>. Als etc. Das
                                                  <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
